  "description": "Curated terminology framework for phenomena at the human–AI interface, with reference tooling and protocol adapters. Formalized as an RDF knowledge graph (SKOS, SKOS-XL, OntoLex-Lemon, SHACL, JSON-LD, TBX). Informed by ISO 704 / ISO 1087 / ISO 30042 (ISO-inspired, not ISO-certified). Descriptive linguistic research, non-peer-reviewed (§11). See DISCLAIMER.md (§1–§20).",
